&lt;p&gt;Here is a list of features it support at this moment:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;configuration deployment&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;secrets deployment&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;SSH bastions&lt;/li&gt;
